description: The most common form of dead emoji simply have Xs for their eyes. You will probably recognize this classic dead emoji, but you can still make it unique by experimenting with all the cool mouth options. For instance, if you use ω for the mouth, the dead emoticon somehow ends up being cute! On the other hand, you can try д or ㅂ to get that gaping mouth look.
